April 4, 2002

This problem actually consists of six different Goma runs
and so it doesn't not fit with the way GUTS works.  So,
I've split the problem into slot.2lyr.[1-6] and disabled
the monolithic problem.   Many more tests are now performed
as a result of the split.  

I'm adding a six sub-problems but it may turn out that only
one or a few are really useful and that intermediate problems
don't exercise different parts of Goma (which is likely so).

Pat Notz

